  "id": "api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy",
  "title": "useStateChangeStrategy",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/ng-observable\", \"name\": \"@zodiac-ui/ng-observable\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy\", \"name\": \"useStateChangeStrategy\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/ng-observable\">@zodiac-ui/ng-observable</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/zodiac-team/zodiac-ui/edit/master/libs/ng-observable/lib/providers.ts?message=docs(ng-observable)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L2-L39\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/zodiac-team/zodiac-ui/tree/master/libs/ng-observable/lib/providers.ts#L2-L39\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"usestatechangestrategy\">useStateChangeStrategy<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy#usestatechangestrategy\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>Configures the change detection strategy for the current injector when used with <a href=\"api/ng-observable/StateFactory\"><code>StateFactory</code></a></p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy#description\">See more...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n  \n  \n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  \n\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy\" class=\"code-anchor\">useStateChangeStrategy</a></span>(strategy: <a href=\"api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy\" class=\"code-anchor\">StateChangeStrategy</a>)</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>strategy</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy\" class=\"code-anchor\">StateChangeStrategy</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p>A flag to determine the change detection strategy that should be used.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n</div>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">See also<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><a href=\"api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy#DETACH\"><code>DETACH</code></a>\n</li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy#REATTACH\"><code>REATTACH</code></a>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>When using <code><a href=\"api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy#DETACH\" class=\"code-anchor\">DETACH</a></code> mode the change detector is detached after the first\nchange detection run and each component must manually call <code><a href=\"api/ng-observable/State\" class=\"code-anchor\">State</a>#<a href=\"api/ng-observable/State#next\" class=\"code-anchor\">next</a></code>\nor <code>ChangeDetectorRef#detectChanges</code> afterwards to\nre-render the template. This behaviour ignores any setting of\n<code>ChangeDetectionStrategy</code> at the compiler or component level. <code><a href=\"api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy#REATTACH\" class=\"code-anchor\">REATTACH</a></code>\nwill reattach the <code>ChangeDetectorRef</code> when the <code><a href=\"api/ng-observable/State\" class=\"code-anchor\">State</a></code> is instantiated.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@Component({\n    providers: [\n        <a href=\"api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy\" class=\"code-anchor\">useStateChangeStrategy</a>(\n            <a href=\"api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy#DETACH\" class=\"code-anchor\">StateChangeStrategy.DETACH</a>, // or <a href=\"api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy#REATTACH\" class=\"code-anchor\">REATTACH</a>\n        ),\n    ],\n})\nexport class AppComponent {}\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/ng-observable\n - guide/ng-observable\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/ng-observable\n - api/ng-observable/State\n - api/ng-observable/State#next\n - api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy\n - api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy#DETACH\n - api/ng-observable/StateChangeStrategy#REATTACH\n - api/ng-observable/StateFactory\n - api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy#description\n - api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy#see-also\n - api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy#usage-notes\n - api/ng-observable/useStateChangeStrategy#usestatechangestrategy\n - https://github.com/zodiac-team/zodiac-ui/edit/master/libs/ng-observable/lib/providers.ts?message=docs(ng-observable)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L2-L39\n - https://github.com/zodiac-team/zodiac-ui/tree/master/libs/ng-observable/lib/providers.ts#L2-L39\n-->"
